<lablist nowrap>
\Tool bar\		Contains the icons for opening the Appointment or
			To Do Editors, and changing the Calendar view.
<newline>&empty;<newline>
\Appt Editor icon\	Opens the Appointment Editor.
\To Do Editor icon\	Opens the To Do Editor.
<newline>&empty;<newline>
\Previous view arrow\	Changes the Calendar view to the previous view (Month 
			view example: from November 1994 to October 1994).
\Today button\		Changes the Calendar view to show the current day.
\Next view arrow\	Changes the Calendar view to the next view (Week view
			example: from "Week Starting Mon, October 17 1994"
			to "Week Starting Mon, October 24 1994".
<newline>&empty;<newline>
\View icons\		Use the view icons to Change the current view 
			to day, week, month, or year view.
<newline>&empty;<newline>
\View label\		Title of day, week, month, or year displayed.
\Calendar view\		Main view of the Calendar.
\Message area\		Displays status messages from Calendar.
<\lablist>

